Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:29.41,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:149416,149416}Tōgō University Hospital{NOTE:東都大学付属病院}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.68,0:02:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152686,152686}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156022,156022}{\i1}No, no. It's impossible\Nfor my teacher to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:36.48,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:156489,156489}Operating room in use
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:38.59,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:158591,158591}Operating room in use
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159426,159426}{\i1}I still have so many things\Nthat I have to learn from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:41.52,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:161528,161528}Operating room in use
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162495,162495}{\i1}Please, don't leave me, Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167334,167334}How is she?\NHow is the operation going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170036,170036}It's been two hours already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:51.07,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:171071,171071}Operating room in use
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172439,172439}Two hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174374,174374}That type of lifestyle…\NIt was just too much for her body to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:02:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179612,179612}Her heart was already bad, and then she had to go through the breakup of Tsukikage Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183683,183683}It sure was too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187420,187420}{\i1}That's right. It's all because of that man from Metropolitan Entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:12.72,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:192726,192726}Operating room in use
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199366,199366}Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200567,200567}How was the surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202068,202068}We did the best we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204137,204137}It's up to her will to live now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212278,212278}Teach—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:41.98,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:221988,221988}Besides the time she spent\Nat school and on stage…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:47.76,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:227761,227761}…Maya spent all her time by Miss Tsukikage,\Nwaiting for her to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:56.43,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:236436,236436}It has been four day since the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248214,248214}If you know of any relatives,\Nplease let them know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253453,253453}If she doesn't regain consciousness tonight,\Nthen she might be through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257323,257323}{\i1}She's… about to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265065,265065}No!\NThat can't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266366,266366}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267200,267200}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269569,269569}You told me you would train me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271705,271705}You told me you would teach me acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274774,274774}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275975,275975}Please, don't take my dream of being "The Crimson Goddess" away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281681,281681}"The Crimson Goddess…"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284584,284584}I can't die… until I finish that project for this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289556,289556}Oh, she's conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291825,291825}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303937,303937}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306906,306906}Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308641,308641}The Actresses who will play "The Crimson Goddess…"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311444,311444}…are you…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313680,313680}…and another.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315582,315582}Another?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316916,316916}Teacher, who is that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318651,318651}You will know soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321154,321154}Here, you need to go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323056,323056}Don't excite her too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325125,325125}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327660,327660}Maya, fight for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329329,329329}If you lose, the other person will take "The Crimson Goddess."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336636,336636}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341374,341374}{\i1}My face is burning,\Nso is my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348948,348948}{\i1}I'm a candidate\Nfor "The Crimson Goddess?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351518,351518}{\i1}I'm always being corrected by her.\NI can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356489,356489}{\i1}My dream is about to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:05:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358792,358792}{\i1}I don't know who this other person is,\Nbut I won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:03.99,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:363997,363997}That day, "Wuthering Heights"\Nhad come to its last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368668,368668}I will die while you will become rich, Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372272,372272}Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373440,373440}Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379612,379612}{\i1}If you love her, watch her\Ntill the end, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384084,384084}{\i1}Maya, why did you want me\Nto come and see your play?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390457,390457}{\i1}I'm hurt to see\Nyour love towards each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409542,409542}I'm hurt that you\Ndidn't even notice me hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:06:57.21,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:417217,417217}Backstage
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417450,417450}Great job!\NYou guys did a wonderful job!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:06:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419486,419486}Can I please get an autograph?\NPlease sign this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424157,424157}Yes, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425725,425725}Ms. Kitajima, any words?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433266,433266}{\i1}Did I lose to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435902,435902}{\i1}No, that's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437604,437604}Ms. Kitajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437804,437804}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439773,439773}Here's a gift for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442008,442008}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:23.44,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:443443,443443}Ms. Kitajima Maya
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443843,443843}{\i1}That's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445745,445745}{\i1}The man who always encourages me with purple roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450850,450850}"Congratulations on the finale of your play."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452585,452585}"I'm glad to see that you get better with each play."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456523,456523}"—Your number one fan,\Nwho is always looking at you."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464698,464698}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465398,465398}Snow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469002,469002}Watch out!\NYou dumb ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469736,469736}Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484751,484751}For Kitajima Maya?\NNo, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486353,486353}B-But, I'm—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488788,488788}I'm told not to let\Nany more fans in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493126,493126}Oh, then, give her this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495295,495295}Give this to Maya, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498531,498531}Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500400,500400}Shoot, what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508141,508141}{\i1}Maya, you have gone somewhere\Nwhere I can't reach you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512512,512512}{\i1}If I only could love someone else.\NThis would have been easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518785,518785}{\i1}So much easier…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:42.12,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:522122,522122}Ms. Kitajima Maya
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522856,522856}{\i1}Mr. Purple Rose,\Nplease watch over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527093,527093}{\i1}I will be a much better actress,\Nand will play "The Crimson Goddess" someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532599,532599}Excuse me, Ms. Kitajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534267,534267}Here, a high school boy\Nleft it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:08:58.57,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:538571,538571}Yū
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541274,541274}Sakurakōji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542909,542909}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547380,547380}{\i1}Catherine…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549749,549749}{\i1}I don't want to end our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551651,551651}{\i1}I will never be able to find a woman like you, Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557357,557357}{\i1}Ryo, you are just going after your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560860,560860}{\i1}Catherine is gone with the stage of "Wuthering Heights."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564698,564698}{\i1}Please realize that soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571204,571204}{\i1}Sakurakōji, why didn't you wait for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575775,575775}{\i1}You didn't stay till the end on the first day either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579946,579946}{\i1}Why didn't you congratulate me on the play's success?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593493,593493}Oh, Mr. President,\Nyou are still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596329,596329}Kitajima Maya was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:09:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599699,599699}You have a great eye\Nfor choosing her, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601901,601901}It was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603203,603203}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604904,604904}Didn't you notice that the childhood Catherine wasn't in sync with the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610076,610076}Well, the critics have written that there's not a smooth
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613380,613380}transition from the childhood Catherine to the adult one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616082,616082}That's right.\NShe doesn't exactly know what acting is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620053,620053}Acting is about team work,\Nand not a one-man play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625091,625091}We won't be able to use her for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627060,627060}That type of actress\Nmesses up the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:34.43,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:634434,634434}Miss Tsukikage's once life-threatening\Ncondition got better and better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.27,0:10:39.27,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:639272,639272}It seems as thought it lost to her passion for "The Crimson Goddess…"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:45.17,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:645178,645178}…and she spent most of her days reading scripts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:50.45,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:650450,650450}The heart of Miss Tsukikage moved\Nfrom her condition to her next play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:10:59.89,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:659893,659893}In the meantime, they have joined Ikkakuju Theater,\Nwho were visiting Tōkyō, and planned for a joint play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:11.43,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:671438,671438}The Smile of Stone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672038,672038}This is our next script.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675475,675475}The Smile of Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677444,677444}Now, I'll announce the casting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684017,684017}Pio, a male swindler: Rei Aoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686553,686553}Huh, a swindler?\NMe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688288,688288}The rich daughter, Marisa,\Nalso Hannah the maid…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692359,692359}…Sayaka Miyazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693493,693493}A double role!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695128,695128}The widow, Frederica: Mina Sawatori.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:36.32,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:696329,696329}The roles were assigned one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698365,698365}The Countess Isabella: Taiko Kasuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700233,700233}Sir Goerge: Satoru Hosoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702936,702936}The attorney, Prefew: Hajime Tabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705171,705171}The relative, Gallison: Taichi Hotta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706806,706806}I wonder what I will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708708,708708}I'm sure you'll play the main role.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711578,711578}Now, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713313,713313}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:11:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718985,718985}I will have you play a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722489,722489}A doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723890,723890}Yes. A doll who just sits\Nin the middle of the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728094,728094}You won't have\Nany movements nor words.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730563,730563}{\i1}Why, why is she giving me\Nsuch a role?
Comment: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:19.78,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:739781,739781}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:23.49,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:743493,743493}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:26.45,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:746454,746454}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752118,752118}I am Prefew, the attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753887,753887}I heard you called for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755689,755689}Mr. Prefew, I wrote a will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758391,758391}I know I only have\Na little time left…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:40.51,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:760510,760510}"The Smile of Stone" is about a 12 year old, Marisa, who is about to die after giving away a large portion of her property to a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:46.43,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:766433,766433}It is a tragic comedy involving a young widow, a countess, a swindler, and many more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:54.84,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:774841,774841}Maya's role is the doll, Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:12:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779279,779279}{\i1}Oh, I want to move,\Nor to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782482,782482}{\i1}This role is no fund,\Njust sitting around like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:06.21,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:786219,786219}Miss Tsukikage started training\Nthe group despite her condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791024,791024}Then, you will walk towards the doll\Nand push onto the doll's shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796296,796296}Very lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799466,799466}Maya!\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801201,801201}You are a doll, not a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803303,803303}If you were a real doll, you would lean forward even thought it was a light touch on the shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806373,806373}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811044,811044}Countess, go and push the doll again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812479,812479}Your elbow bent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813747,813747}A doll wouldn't try to cover her body, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817650,817650}Do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821888,821888}Your hip!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822822,822822}A doll wouldn't fall on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825358,825358}Why would you open your eyes when falling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827560,827560}A doll doesn't have an expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829496,829496}Your body is too soft.\NDo it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833533,833533}Straighten your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835935,835935}Your neck again.\NDo it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849983,849983}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851518,851518}This is not good for your body.\NWe should finish for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854387,854387}No!\NMaya, continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857524,857524}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872939,872939}I didn't think that the role of a doll\Nwould be this difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875842,875842}Well, in this situation,\NI'll become a doll, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880980,880980}Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881381,881381}It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882582,882582}Let me hold her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883750,883750}No, you already held her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896162,896162}Become a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:901267,901267}Big sister,\Ncan we have our doll back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923456,923456}Mama, there's a crazy lady here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926159,926159}I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970503,970503}Would a doll\Nchange her facial expression?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972906,972906}I got the doll's pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975075,975075}But, I can't…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977577,977577}I can't quite get the movement of a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:991758,991758}Well, but it's too bad that Miss Tsukikage can't come here and train us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997530,997530}It's a critical time for her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000834,1000834}I hope she'll get better by the day of the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003436,1003436}That's why she needs to rest now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:16:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018051,1018051}Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020687,1020687}Teacher, shouldn't you be back at the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023723,1023723}I know, if your condition gets worse…\NRight, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029496,1029496}I'm okay.\NHere, let's get to training.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032699,1032699}Maya, come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045578,1045578}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047580,1047580}I thought you would be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050517,1050517}Please go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052986,1052986}I wouldn't want you\Nto die just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062429,1062429}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063029,1063029}Let her get up by herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064597,1064597}Mr. Masumi, don't help her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068368,1068368}What's going on with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076209,1076209}Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:17:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078044,1078044}No, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:17:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079512,1079512}Don't.\NTake it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096663,1096663}What is this all about,\NMiss Tsukikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099065,1099065}She's learning the difference between the body of a human and that of a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103169,1103169}Humans have numerous joints,\Nbut dolls only have about five.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108008,1108008}By putting bamboo all around her body,\Nshe can't use her human joints anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112379,1112379}This doll cast should teach her\Nthe movement of a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116583,1116583}A doll cast…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118818,1118818}You didn't have to do this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122655,1122655}Hurry! Take her to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124224,1124224}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128361,1128361}What the hell are you guys thinking?\NYou and her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131598,1131598}Mr. Masumi, has your father ever told you\Nthe story about my childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136636,1136636}A little.\NI know your parents died young…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:18:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139973,1139973}…and so you had to go\Nthrough many hardships.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143009,1143009}I might have been dead, if Ozaki Ichiren\Ndidn't give me a reason to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149482,1149482}A reason to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151117,1151117}Acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152919,1152919}Because of acting,\NI am able to live, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157991,1157991}I want to give her\Nthe same reason to live, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166833,1166833}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168234,1168234}Listen, don't do too much of anything just because your wounds are not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170904,1170904}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172238,1172238}No bathing,\Nnor moving your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175575,1175575}Yes, I know.\NThanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176943,1176943}Does she really know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180146,1180146}I don't want to hear any more about what I can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186886,1186886}Little girl,\Nlet me give you a ride home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189089,1189089}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190256,1190256}I'd rather walk\Nthan have you give me a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193460,1193460}You should accept it when people offer you things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200200,1200200}You are so pushy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201835,1201835}I'm not trying to hurt you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203737,1203737}I just want to take you home safely, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206473,1206473}I'm not a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208274,1208274}I'm about to graduate\Nfrom junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211578,1211578}And which high school\Nare you going to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213880,1213880}I'm not. I'm going to practice acting\Nwhile working at a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217717,1217717}If you want to act, then you will need\Nat least a high school education.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221287,1221287}You should take school\Nmore seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224991,1224991}How do you think I can afford it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227727,1227727}I don't have that luxury.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229562,1229562}Get away from Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231631,1231631}Metropolitan Entertainment will make you a great actress, while supplying you with a scholarship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238138,1238138}That was what you had planned, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240507,1240507}I won't do it\Neven if I was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244477,1244477}Even if you were dead…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255855,1255855}Okay, take care of your wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260827,1260827}Screw Metropolitan Entertainment!\NYou snob!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268301,1268301}That reminded me about high school,\Nthought I was ready to give up…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281881,1281881}Manpuku Ken
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283650,1283650}Here, ramen and a potsticker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285051,1285051}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294060,1294060}Haru, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296129,1296129}Can't you do something\Nabout that cough?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297464,1297464}You're scaring the customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300600,1300600}Haru, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:51.31,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1311311,1311311}Principal's office
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312345,1312345}What?\NI'm going to high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:21:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313613,1313613}Some noble man said\Nhe would take care of everything…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.45,0:21:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1317450,1317450}…from tuition to board,\Nfor the reputable Hitotsuboshi High.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321354,1321354}Hitotsuboshi High?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.18,0:22:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1323189,1323189}They have great acting programs…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1325992,1325992}…but, who in the world\Ndid something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329529,1329529}Well, I didn't meet him,\Nbut he left something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.97,0:22:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1337971,1337971}{\i1}That's him!\NMr. Purple Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.74,0:22:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1341741,1341741}"Please accept my good intentions."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1344110,1344110}"I'm sure you will be able to learn acting while enjoying your high school days."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1351451,1351451}{\i1}"Looking forward to seeing you grow as an actress."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.72,0:22:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1356723,1356723}Mr. Purple Rose,\Nplease keep looking after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.22,0:22:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1360226,1360226}I'll do it.\NI'll make it happen.
